.TH wxControl 3 "wx 2.5.4" "Ericsson AB" "Erlang Module Definition"
.SH NAME
wxControl \- This is the base class for a control or "widget".

.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
A control is generally a small window which processes user input and/or displays one or more item of data.

